{"tid":2450030,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日擺術站撚到個黑驚呆左","createTime":"2021-03-17T05:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T08:51:13.000Z","uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"95c786b9742bab3f7bdb32c9d4b6ae102ef1432d","tid":2450030,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"話說今朝早我要去塘頭塘擺刮站<br />\n咁我就想被罷工 冇出到門口<br />\n仲睇緊大香港早餐 就馬上收到我上司 王姑娘既電話問我係邊<br />\n<br />\n我因為驚比上司罵所以即刻趕番去<br />\n去到途中比幾隻防暴截住我話要查我 又罵我甲由又剩<br />\n我見佢地咁嬲 我係褲袋拎左粒陳年可樂糖出黎諗住安撫佢地<br />\n防暴狗即刻問我比粒糖佢地做咩 問我係咪弱智<br />\n<br />\n我諗都唔諗就答係<br />\n<br />\n班狗全部冇聲出呆撚晒 我就借啲意跑走左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過見到有個工友(金興正)好似比人拉走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0153a4352677179d81d9e88bf3d83cdd9c14c85","tid":2450030,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"拉暴樓煮。"},{"pid":"a02567c6ec695ab9a0d2c8e85891fc0de58df8eb","tid":2450030,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863c4999a9f4a1f97edc9a46775165fc7c8ca7ba","tid":2450030,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"樓主係熱狗 拉"},{"pid":"61434d4a2e1356858997ed9538a072b0a67dd5c2","tid":2450030,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:56:13.000Z","msg":"點你老針， 賴低我自己走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f2d528292bd6f21d4bff7ae0392480b9eab4e4","tid":2450030,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"屈撚夠未"},{"pid":"1aeff3cc4160d8b72f978ff6e88bf6ed88246cdd","tid":2450030,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 